**Node Layer** (Zephyr RTOS):
ESP32-S3 (WiFi6/BLE 5.0) + CC1352R (Sub-GHz backup)
Records: EEG + RF params → local flash (AES-256)

**Bluetooth LE** (<10m):
Nodes → Phone NVMe (Shamir 3-of-2)
Payload: threshold_signed bundles (139 bytes)

**WiFi6** (192.168.1.134 → 100m):
Phone → NEURAL_GATEWAY (Ubuntu server)
SQLite + Prometheus monitoring

**Cellular** (Tower/Sat backup):
EID burst → XRPL Hooks (0.001 XRP/bundle)
Satellite: Iridium SBD (emergency only)